# Implementation Plan - Phase 1: Special Discounts

This plan outlines the design and implementation for **Phase 1: Special Discounts** as outlined in the recommendations document. It adds the capability to apply unit-level discounts at checkout while enforcing role-based permissions (limits for staff, unlimited for owner).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Staff Discount Limits**: By default, staff discounts are capped at **₹50 per item (unit)**. This limit will be configurable under **Settings > Receipt & Billing Settings** by the store owner.
> - **Net Revenue & Analytics**: Profit and revenue trends on the analytics page will now reflect **Net Revenue** (revenue after discounts) rather than Gross Revenue.

